ZH: 我昨天在超市里碰见了我的老师。
EN: I ran into my teacher at the supermarket yesterday.

ZH: 他们在图书馆里碰见了对方。
EN: They met each other at the library.

ZH: 我们在公园里碰见了一只狗。
EN: We encountered a dog in the park.

ZH: 你会在派对上碰见其他同学。
EN: You will meet other classmates at the party.

ZH: 她在车站里碰见了一个老朋友。
EN: She encountered an old friend at the train station.

ZH: 孩子们经常在学校里碰见彼此。
EN: The children often run into each other at school.

ZH: 他们突然在街上碰见了一个明星。
EN: Suddenly they spotted a celebrity on the street.

ZH: 昨天我在街上碰见了我的邻居。
EN: Yesterday I bumped into my neighbor on the street.

ZH: 我们在咖啡店里碰见了一个作家。
EN: We met a writer at the coffee shop.

ZH: 他们在海边碰见了一群海豚。
EN: They encountered a group of dolphins at the seaside.

ZH: 我们在这个城市里碰见了很多有趣的事物。
EN: We met many interesting things in this city.

ZH: 我们在山上碰见了一个野生生物学家。
EN: We encountered a wildlife biologist on the mountain.

ZH: 他们在博物馆里碰见了一个艺术家。
EN: They met an artist at the museum.

ZH: 我们在火车站里碰见了一个乞丐。
EN: We encountered a beggar at the train station.

ZH: 春天，你会在公园里碰见很多鸟类。
EN: In spring, you will encounter many birds in the park.

ZH: 我们在大街上碰见了一个老人。
EN: We bumped into an old man on the main street.

